# ESP-IDF build artifacts
build/
sdkconfig
sdkconfig.old
managed_components/

# Wave 14 W14-H15: IDF Component Manager generates dependencies.lock with
# absolute paths for any locally-cloned (type: local) component. The path
# bakes in the dev-machine layout (e.g. /home/rebelforce/...) which makes
# CI completely unable to resolve components. Component Manager regenerates
# a fresh lock from main/idf_component.yml during idf.py reconfigure, so
# dropping this file from version control costs nothing — each developer
# and CI get their own valid lock on checkout.
dependencies.lock

